The IPSC Timer is designed for IPSC & IDPA practical shooters. Besides standard timer features this app displays the elapsed time and the splits between the fired shots. It's always with you whenever you and your iPhone are.
This app has a unique shot recognition algorithm which works properly indoor and outdoor. It's ideal for competition, training and coaching in any conditions.
The IPSC Timer has many useful advantages in comparison with the standard ones. You can replay and save the training results and its soundtracks in your iPhone. This feature is especially helpful during competitions when it is important to avoid any mistakes.
The price and functionality of the Timer is incomparable with standard, sometimes bulky devices.

Main features:

- IPSC Timer detects the shots and shows its timing using internal iPhone capabilities;
- the best results are reached when using Iphone 5 or higher;
- time splits between shots;
- number of shoots;
- random or specific signal delay;
- indoor & outdoor shots detection;
- saves and e-mails the result: score, hitfactor and soundtracks of trainings;
- playback current or stored trainings.

Do you want to know how fast does your car accelerate to 100 km/h?
It’s not a secret, that data of producer is approximate and apply only for ideal conditions. To know the current speed here and now, to make a measure 0-100 km/h, 100-200 km/h, time for ¼ miles ( time of passing 402 meters) will help you the application Test-Drive.
You don’t need any additional devices as RaceLogic, because you already have the accelerometer sensor and GPS sensor in your smartphone. Due to these super sensitive sensors of your iPhone and unique algorithm, we have got am opportunity to measure the time of acceleration of the car to the necessary speed with a high accuracy.
Opportunities of the application:
          - acceleration to 100 km/h;
          - acceleration from 100 to 200 km/h;
          - acceleration to 80 km/h;
          - acceleration from 80 to 120 km/h;
          - time of passing 402 meters and 1000 meters;
          - understandable interface;
          - constant updates and expansion of the functional;
          - the results of the measures save automatically and you can share them with your friends!

